      "para_id": "Q001436.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ninlil , Ur-saga , the ... scribe of Enlil’s temple , dedicated this ( vase ) as a votive offering for the life of Irina-badbi , the temple administrator of Enlil , for the well-being of Ama-abzi , and for the well being of his spouse and child ."
    }
  ],
